==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Cocoa
<hw>Co"coa</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Corrupted fr.
<ets>cacao</ets>.]</ety> <def>A preparation made from the seeds of the
chocolate tree, and used in making, a beverage; also the beverage made
from cocoa or cocoa shells.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Cocoa shells</b></col>, <cd>the husks which separate from
the cacao seeds in preparing them for use.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

